   STAR BANC Corp. (Cincinnati) -- John C. (Jack) Dannemiller
was elected a director of this banking concern, succeeding
Mark T. Johnson, who retired in July. Mr. Dannemiller is
president, chief operating officer and a director of Bearings
Inc., Cleveland.
