8.15% fixed-rate notes due Sept. 18, 1992, priced at par.
When-issued trading will begin today. Settlement will be
Thursday. Interest payments will be made semiannually
beginning March 18, 1991. The notes are sold through a
selling group managed by Sallie Mae and are available in book
entry form.
   Farm Credit System Financial Assistance Corp. -- $89
million of 15-year 9.20% fixed-rate optional principal
