   Motor vehicles, parts and accessories ........... $18.9
   Machinery, engines and boilers .................. $15.3
   Electrical equipment ............................ $ 7.3
                                                                                                       

   Pct. of U.S. exports that go to Canada ..........   24%
   Pct. of Canada's imports that come from U.S. ....   65%
                                                                                                       

