ELECTRIC UTILITIES (ELC)
</IN>
<LP>
   Portland General Corp. has signed a definitive agreement
to acquire as much as 49% of the common stock of Bonneville
Pacific Corp., an independent energy, food processing and
waste management concern, for about $34 million.
   Portland General, an energy holding company in Portland,
Ore., will buy a $10 million debenture convertible into 1.3
